  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct. The FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two independent laboratories. The intended use is pre-market submission support for a Class II spinal fixation device under 21 CFR 888.3070, specifically to substantiate structural adequacy under worst-case surgical loading. All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors have been assessed; the Test Conditions factor achieved one gradation below the required level owing to evaluation at a single load angle. Overall credibility is judged sufficient for the stated submission purpose.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/nagaraja-f1717-compression-bending-req-001",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/nagaraja-fea-f1717-static-cb-claim-001",
